        <Parent_String>azimuthal projection (technique) [300263983], projection (perspective and shading technique) [300053420], perspective and shading techniques [300053413], image-making processes and techniques [300053159], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
